<div class="student-panel--content">
  <p class="block-lead-in">The Department of Electrical and Computer Engineering (ECE) at the University of Maryland, College Park offers one of the strongest and most highly-ranked programs in the nation. </p>
  <a href="https://ece.umd.edu/research" class="button button--hollow-red">Explore our Research Programs</a></div>
						</div>
						<div class="col-large-6">
              

<div class="student-panel--media">
	<figure><img typeof="foaf:Image" src="https://ece.umd.edu/sites/ece.umd.edu/files/ece-about-800x500.jpg" width="800" height="500" alt="Student in blue and white checked shirt adjusts equipment in microelectronics lab." /></figure>
